  "texts": [
    "ConclusionExamining useful applications of prompt engineering for Large Language Models (LLMs) in banking & e-commerce shows that the careful design of prompts may significantly affect the usefulness, accuracy & the reliability of AI systems.",
    "Rapid engineering improves customer service efficiency in banks, speeds fraud detection & supports regulatory compliance.",
    "In e-commerce, well crafted prompts are improving product recommendations, enabling better customizing, and increasing customer contact across systems.",
    "The unifying thread running throughout these successes is the need of fast engineering as the means of bridging natural AI capacity with practical economic advantage.",
    "It's not simply about letting LLMs generate meaningful language; it's also about matching AI behavior to context, goals & also user expectations."
  ],
